<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Perfect Job Match Found!</title>
    <style>
        body { 
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; 
            line-height: 1.6; 
            color: #333; 
            margin: 0; 
            padding: 0; 
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
        }
        .container { 
            max-width: 600px; 
            margin: 0 auto; 
            background-color: white; 
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header { 
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10B981, #059669); 
            color: white; 
            padding: 40px 30px; 
            text-align: center; 
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; 
        }
        .header h1 { 
            margin: 0; 
            font-size: 28px; 
            font-weight: 700; 
        }
        .match-score {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .match-percentage {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .match-label {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            margin: 5px 0 0 0;
        }
        .content { 
            background: #ffffff; 
            padding: 40px 30px; 
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #374151;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        .job-card { 
            background: #f8fafc; 
            border: 2px solid #e5e7eb; 
            border-radius: 12px; 
            padding: 25px; 
            margin: 25px 0; 
        }
        .job-title {
            color: #1f2937;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
        }
        .job-details {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 10px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .job-detail {
            color: #4b5563;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .job-detail strong {
            color: #1f2937;
        }
        .description {
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 15px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border-left: 4px solid #10B981;
        }
        .match-reasons {
            background: #ecfdf5;
            border: 1px solid #a7f3d0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .match-reasons h4 {
            color: #065f46;
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .reason-list {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .reason-list li {
            color: #047857;
            margin: 8px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .button { 
            display: inline-block; 
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10B981, #059669);
            color: white; 
            padding: 16px 32px; 
            text-decoration: none; 
            border-radius: 8px; 
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.25);
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .personalized-note {
            background: #fef3c7;
            border: 1px solid #f59e0b;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            color: #92400e;
        }
        .footer { 
            background: #f9fafb;
            text-align: center; 
            padding: 30px; 
            color: #6b7280; 
            font-size: 12px; 
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #10B981;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .stat-item {
            background: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .stat-value {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #10B981;
        }
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🎯 Perfect Job Match Found!</h1>
            {{#if matchPercentage}}
            <div class="match-score">
                <p class="match-percentage">{{matchPercentage}}%</p>
                <p class="match-label">Profile Match Score</p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                <p>Hi {{userProfile.name}},</p>
                <p>Exciting news! We found a job opportunity that's an excellent match for your profile.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="job-card">
                <h3 class="job-title">{{title}}</h3>
                
                <div class="job-details">
                    <div class="job-detail">
                        <strong>🏢 Company:</strong> {{company}}
                    </div>
                    <div class="job-detail">
                        <strong>📍 Location:</strong> {{location}}
                    </div>
                    <div class="job-detail">
                        <strong>💼 Type:</strong> {{type}}
                    </div>
                    <div class="job-detail">
                        <strong>🎓 For:</strong> {{userProfile.qualification}} {{userProfile.stream}}
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="description">
                    <strong>Job Description:</strong><br>
                    {{description}}
                </div>
            </div>
            
            {{#if matchReasons}}
            <div class="match-reasons">
                <h4>🎯 Why This Job is Perfect for You:</h4>
                <ul class="reason-list">
                    {{#each matchReasons}}
                    <li>{{this}}</li>
                    {{/each}}
                </ul>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            {{#if userProfile.cgpa}}
            <div class="personalized-note">
                <strong>💡 Personalized Note:</strong> With your {{userProfile.cgpa}} CGPA in {{userProfile.stream}}, you're a strong candidate for this position. Your academic background aligns perfectly with their requirements!
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <div class="cta-section">
                <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Ready to take the next step in your career?</p>
                <a href="{{applicationLink}}" class="button">🚀 Apply Now</a>
                <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">
                    <em>Apply quickly - the best opportunities don't last long!</em>
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="stats-grid">
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-value">{{matchPercentage}}%</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Profile Match</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-value">{{userProfile.qualification}}</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Your Qualification</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">
                Best regards,<br>
                <strong style="color: #10B981;">The XCareer Team</strong><br>
                <em>Connecting talent with opportunities</em>
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>© 2024 XCareer. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>You received this email because your profile matches this job opportunity.</p>
            <p><a href="#">Unsubscribe</a> | <a href="#">Update Preferences</a> | <a href="#">View More Jobs</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
